com.facebook.accountkit.internal

Class FacebookAppEventLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.accountkit.internal.FacebookAppEventLogger

  • public class FacebookAppEventLogger
extends java.lang.Object
    This class send event over to Facebook SDK if exists to log App Events for analytics. If proguard is used, the following rules must be added: -keep class com.facebook.FacebookSdk { boolean isInitialized(); } -keep class com.facebook.appevents.AppEventsLogger { com.facebook.appevents.AppEventsLogger newLogger(android.content.Context); void logSdkEvent(java.lang.String, java.lang.Double, android.os.Bundle); }
